---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<Layout
  title="Pondok Pesantren Al Usmani | Penerimaan Santri 2026/2027"
  description="Penerimaan santri Pondok Pesantren Baitul Ulum Wal Huffadz Al Usmani di Ciledug, Tangerang. Program Tahfidz, Diniyyah, TPQ, bahasa, dan pembentukan adab."
>
  <main>
    <!-- ═══ HEADER ═══ -->
    <header class="site-header" id="site-header">
      <a class="brand" href="#home" aria-label="Al Usmani, halaman utama">
        <img class="brand-logo" src="/images/logo.jpeg" alt="Logo Al Usmani" />
        <span class="brand-text">
          <strong>AL USMANI</strong>
          <small>Baitul 'Ulum Wal Huffadz</small>
        </span>
      </a>
      <nav class="nav-links" aria-label="Navigasi utama">
        <a href="#tentang">Tentang</a>
        <a href="#program">Program</a>
        <a href="#kehidupan">Kehidupan Santri</a>
        <a href="#lokasi">Lokasi</a>
        <a class="nav-cta" href="#daftar">Daftar Sekarang →</a>
      </nav>
      <button class="menu-button" id="menu-toggle" aria-label="Buka menu" aria-expanded="false">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 5h16"/><path d="M4 12h16"/><path d="M4 19h16"/></svg>
      </button>
    </header>

    <!-- Mobile Menu -->
    <div class="mobile-menu" id="mobile-menu">
      <button class="mobile-menu-close" id="menu-close" aria-label="Tutup menu">✕</button>
      <a href="#tentang">Tentang</a>
      <a href="#program">Program</a>
      <a href="#kehidupan">Kehidupan Santri</a>
      <a href="#lokasi">Lokasi</a>
      <a href="#daftar">Daftar Sekarang</a>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══ HERO ═══ -->
    <section class="hero" id="home">
      <div class="hero-copy reveal">
        <div class="eyebrow">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M11.017 2.814a1 1 0 0 1 1.966 0l1.051 5.558a2 2 0 0 0 1.594 1.594l5.558 1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0 1.966l-5.558 1.051a2 2 0 0 0-1.594 1.594l-1.051 5.558a1 1 0 0 1-1.966 0l-1.051-5.558a2 2 0 0 0-1.594-1.594l-5.558-1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0-1.966l5.558-1.051a2 2 0 0 0 1.594-1.594z"/><path d="M20 2v4"/><path d="M22 4h-4"/></svg>
          Penerimaan Santri 2026/2027 Dibuka
        </div>
        <h1>Tumbuh dalam ilmu.<br /><em>Berakar dalam adab.</em></h1>
        <p class="hero-lead">
          Mendampingi putra-putri menjadi generasi Qur'ani yang berilmu, percaya
          diri, dan siap membawa manfaat bagi umat.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a class="button-primary" href="#daftar">
            Mulai Pendaftaran
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a class="text-link" href="#program">
            Jelajahi program
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-trust">
          <p>
            <strong>Muqim atau pulang-pergi</strong><br />
            Pilihan belajar sesuai kebutuhan keluarga
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-visual reveal">
        <div class="hero-image-wrap">
          <img src="/images/logo.jpeg" alt="Logo Pondok Pesantren Al Usmani" />
        </div>
        <div class="arabic-orbit" aria-hidden="true">العلم نور</div>
        <div class="hero-note">
          <span>Sejak langkah pertama</span>
          <strong>Menjadi rumah untuk belajar &amp; bertumbuh</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ MARQUEE ═══ -->
    <section class="marquee-strip" aria-label="Nilai utama Al Usmani">
      <div>
        <span>ILMU</span><i>✦</i>
        <span>ADAB</span><i>✦</i>
        <span>AL-QUR'AN</span><i>✦</i>
        <span>ISTIQAMAH</span><i>✦</i>
        <span>KEBERANIAN</span><i>✦</i>
        <span>MANFAAT</span><i>✦</i>
        <span>ILMU</span><i>✦</i>
        <span>ADAB</span><i>✦</i>
        <span>AL-QUR'AN</span><i>✦</i>
        <span>ISTIQAMAH</span><i>✦</i>
        <span>KEBERANIAN</span><i>✦</i>
        <span>MANFAAT</span><i>✦</i>
        <span>ILMU</span><i>✦</i>
        <span>ADAB</span><i>✦</i>
        <span>AL-QUR'AN</span><i>✦</i>
        <span>ISTIQAMAH</span><i>✦</i>
        <span>KEBERANIAN</span><i>✦</i>
        <span>MANFAAT</span><i>✦</i>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ ABOUT ═══ -->
    <section class="intro section" id="tentang">
      <div class="section-label">01 / Tentang Kami</div>
      <div class="intro-grid">
        <div class="reveal">
          <p class="kicker">Pendidikan yang menyentuh akal dan hati</p>
          <h2>Bukan sekadar menghafal, tetapi <em>menjadi pribadi yang berilmu dan beradab.</em></h2>
        </div>
        <div class="intro-body reveal">
          <p>
            Pondok Pesantren Baitul 'Ulum Wal Huffadz Al Usmani menghadirkan
            lingkungan belajar yang memadukan Al-Qur'an, ilmu agama, bahasa,
            keterampilan, dan pembentukan karakter.
          </p>
          <p>
            Setiap santri didampingi untuk memahami ilmu, mengamalkannya dalam
            keseharian, lalu berani menyampaikannya dengan santun dan penuh
            percaya diri.
          </p>
          <a class="text-link dark" href="#kehidupan">
            Lihat keseharian santri
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="intro-quote reveal">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="34" height="34" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z"/><path d="M5 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z"/></svg>
        <p>"Menuntut ilmu adalah jalan menuju kemuliaan dunia dan akhirat."</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ PROGRAMS ═══ -->
    <section class="program-section section" id="program">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <div>
          <div class="section-label light">02 / Program Pendidikan</div>
          <p class="kicker light">Jalan belajar yang utuh</p>
          <h2>Bekal untuk hari ini.<br /><em>Cahaya untuk nanti.</em></h2>
        </div>
        <p>
          Kurikulum dirancang untuk menyeimbangkan kedalaman ilmu, kebiasaan
          baik, kecakapan bahasa, dan keberanian tampil.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="program-grid">
        <article class="program-card reveal">
          <span class="program-number">01</span>
          <svg class="program-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="31" height="31" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 7v14"/><path d="M3 18a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h5a4 4 0 0 1 4 4 4 4 0 0 1 4-4h5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v13a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-6a3 3 0 0 0-3 3 3 3 0 0 0-3-3z"/></svg>
          <h3>Tahfidz Al-Qur'an</h3>
          <p>
            Membangun kedekatan dengan Al-Qur'an melalui hafalan, tahsin, tajwid,
            dan pembiasaan ibadah yang istiqamah.
          </p>
          <a href="#daftar" aria-label="Daftar untuk program Tahfidz Al-Qur'an">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </article>
        <article class="program-card reveal">
          <span class="program-number">02</span>
          <svg class="program-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="31" height="31" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 5h4"/><path d="M20 3v4"/><path d="M20.985 12.486a9 9 0 1 1-9.473-9.472c.405-.022.617.46.402.803a6 6 0 0 0 8.268 8.268c.344-.215.825-.004.803.401"/></svg>
          <h3>Diniyyah 'Alim</h3>
          <p>
            Pendalaman aqidah, fiqih, hadits, sejarah, adab, serta Nahwu Shorof
            untuk santri putri usia 13 tahun ke atas.
          </p>
          <a href="#daftar" aria-label="Daftar untuk program Diniyyah 'Alim">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </article>
        <article class="program-card reveal">
          <span class="program-number">03</span>
          <svg class="program-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="31" height="31" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m5 8 6 6"/><path d="m4 14 6-6 2-3"/><path d="M2 5h12"/><path d="M7 2h1"/><path d="m22 22-5-10-5 10"/><path d="M14 18h6"/></svg>
          <h3>Bahasa &amp; Percaya Diri</h3>
          <p>
            Bahasa Arab, Bahasa Inggris, muhadharah, presentasi, dan pengalaman
            mengajar untuk menumbuhkan keberanian.
          </p>
          <a href="#daftar" aria-label="Daftar untuk program Bahasa & Percaya Diri">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </article>
      </div>
      <div class="curriculum-row reveal">
        <span>Yang dipelajari</span>
        <div>
          <span>Tahfidz &amp; Tahsin</span>
          <span>Kitab Kuning</span>
          <span>Fiqih &amp; Hadits</span>
          <span>Aqidah &amp; Akhlak</span>
          <span>Bahasa Arab</span>
          <span>Bahasa Inggris</span>
          <span>Nahwu Shorof</span>
          <span>Muhadharah</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ JOURNEY ═══ -->
    <section class="journey section">
      <div class="section-label">03 / Perjalanan Santri</div>
      <div class="journey-grid">
        <div class="journey-image reveal">
          <img src="/images/gallery-5.webp" alt="Kegiatan belajar di Al Usmani" />
          <span class="image-caption">Belajar dengan tekun, bertumbuh dengan gembira.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="journey-copy reveal">
          <p class="kicker">Didampingi di setiap proses</p>
          <h2>Ritme yang membentuk <em>kebiasaan baik.</em></h2>
          <div class="journey-list">
            <div>
              <span>1</span>
              <p>
                <strong>Kenali potensi</strong>
                Setiap anak datang dengan cerita, kemampuan, dan ritme belajar
                yang berbeda.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span>2</span>
              <p>
                <strong>Bangun kebiasaan</strong>
                Ibadah, belajar, disiplin, dan adab dilatih dalam keseharian yang
                terarah.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span>3</span>
              <p>
                <strong>Berani bermanfaat</strong>
                Santri dilatih tampil, berbicara, mengajar, dan hadir untuk
                lingkungannya.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ GALLERY ═══ -->
    <section class="gallery-section section" id="kehidupan">
      <div class="gallery-heading">
        <div>
          <div class="section-label">04 / Kehidupan Santri</div>
          <p class="kicker">Hari-hari yang penuh makna</p>
          <h2>Belajar. Bertumbuh.<br /><em>Bersama.</em></h2>
        </div>
        <a
          class="instagram-link"
          href="https://www.instagram.com/ponpes_al_usmani/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
        >
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="20" height="20" x="2" y="2" rx="5" ry="5"/><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"/><line x1="17.5" x2="17.51" y1="6.5" y2="6.5"/></svg>
          Ikuti @ponpes_al_usmani
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="gallery-grid">
        <figure class="gallery-tall reveal">
          <img src="/images/gallery-7.jpg" alt="Kebersamaan yang menguatkan" loading="lazy" />
          <figcaption>Kebersamaan yang menguatkan</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure class="gallery-square reveal">
          <img src="/images/gallery-5.webp" alt="Belajar tahsin bersama" loading="lazy" />
          <figcaption>Tumbuh melalui proses</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure class="gallery-square reveal">
          <img src="/images/gallery-3.webp" alt="Tumbuh melalui proses" loading="lazy" />
          <figcaption>Bergabung bersama Al Usmani</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure class="gallery-wide reveal">
          <img src="/images/gallery-6.jpg" alt="Berani tampil dan berkarya" loading="lazy" />
          <figcaption>Berani tampil dan berkarya</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ LOCATION ═══ -->
    <section class="location-section section" id="lokasi">
      <div class="location-card">
        <div class="location-copy">
          <div class="section-label light">05 / Lokasi</div>
          <p class="kicker light">Dekat dari rumah, hangat seperti rumah</p>
          <h2>Temukan kami<br />di <em>Ciledug.</em></h2>
          <div class="address-block">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
            <p>
              <strong>Yayasan Baitul Ulum Wal Huffadz Al Usmani</strong>
              Jl. Wiru Indah I, Parung Serab, Ciledug, Kota Tangerang, Banten
            </p>
          </div>
          <a
            class="button-light"
            href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/2SPWoviGf1VFaN6f9"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noreferrer"
          >
            Buka Google Maps
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="map-wrap">
          <iframe
            title="Lokasi Pondok Pesantren Al Usmani"
            src="https://www.google.com/maps?q=-6.2504014,106.699155&z=17&output=embed"
            loading="lazy"
            referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
          ></iframe>
          <div class="map-pin-label">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 5h4"/><path d="M20 3v4"/><path d="M20.985 12.486a9 9 0 1 1-9.473-9.472c.405-.022.617.46.402.803a6 6 0 0 0 8.268 8.268c.344-.215.825-.004.803.401"/></svg>
            Al Usmani
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ REGISTRATION ═══ -->
    <section class="admission-section section" id="daftar">
      <div class="admission-intro reveal">
        <div class="section-label">06 / Pendaftaran</div>
        <p class="kicker">Awali langkah baik hari ini</p>
        <h2>Mari bertumbuh<br /><em>bersama Al Usmani.</em></h2>
        <p>
          Ceritakan kebutuhan putra-putri Anda. Tim penerimaan menghubungi
          kembali untuk konsultasi program, jadwal kunjungan, dan langkah
          selanjutnya.
        </p>
        <div class="admission-points">
          <div>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="21" height="21" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
            <span><strong>Konsultasi awal</strong> tanpa biaya</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="21" height="21" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><path d="M16 3.128a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.744"/><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
            <span>Pilihan <strong>muqim atau pulang-pergi</strong></span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="21" height="21" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 9.5a5.5 5.5 0 0 1 9.591-3.676.56.56 0 0 0 .818 0A5.49 5.49 0 0 1 22 9.5c0 2.29-1.5 4-3 5.5l-5.492 5.313a2 2 0 0 1-3 .019L5 15c-1.5-1.5-3-3.2-3-5.5"/></svg>
            <span>Pendampingan sejak <strong>proses pendaftaran</strong></span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a
          class="whatsapp-inline"
          href="https://wa.me/6281779055909"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
        >
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="19" height="19" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2.992 16.342a2 2 0 0 1 .094 1.167l-1.065 3.29a1 1 0 0 0 1.236 1.168l3.413-.998a2 2 0 0 1 1.099.092 10 10 0 1 0-4.777-4.719"/></svg>
          Atau hubungi WhatsApp 0817 7905 5909
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="form-card reveal">
        <form name="penerimaan-santri" id="registration-form">
          <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="penerimaan-santri" />
          <p class="honeypot">
            <label>Jangan isi bagian ini: <input name="bot-field" /></label>
          </p>
          <div class="form-heading">
            <span>Form minat pendaftaran</span>
            <strong>± 2 menit</strong>
          </div>
          <label>
            Nama orang tua / wali
            <input type="text" placeholder="Contoh: Bapak Ahmad" required name="parentName" />
          </label>
          <label>
            Nomor WhatsApp
            <input type="tel" inputmode="tel" placeholder="08xx xxxx xxxx" required name="phone" />
          </label>
          <div class="form-row">
            <label>
              Nama calon santri
              <input type="text" placeholder="Nama lengkap" required name="studentName" />
            </label>
            <label>
              Usia
              <input type="number" min="4" max="30" placeholder="Tahun" required name="age" />
            </label>
          </div>
          <div class="form-row">
            <label>
              Program diminati
              <select name="program" required>
                <option value="" disabled selected>Pilih program</option>
                <option>Tahfidz Al-Qur'an</option>
                <option>Diniyyah 'Alim Putri</option>
                <option>TPQ Al Usmani</option>
                <option>Belum yakin, ingin konsultasi</option>
              </select>
            </label>
            <label>
              Sistem belajar
              <select name="attendance" required>
                <option value="" disabled selected>Pilih sistem</option>
                <option>Muqim</option>
                <option>Pulang-pergi</option>
                <option>Ingin konsultasi</option>
              </select>
            </label>
          </div>
          <label>
            Yang ingin ditanyakan <span class="optional">(opsional)</span>
            <textarea name="notes" rows="3" placeholder="Biaya, jadwal, fasilitas, atau kebutuhan khusus..."></textarea>
          </label>
          <button class="button-primary form-submit" type="submit">
            Kirim Minat Pendaftaran
